---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const post = {
  title: 'Lockers for Sale- PlayerStall',
  description: 'Quality wood lockers for sale—30+ years. Custom sports lockers for teams and home. Lifetime guarantee. Free consultation. PlayerStall has the right lockers for you.',
  category: 'Buying Guides',
  datePublished: '2017-05-21',
  readTime: '4 min read',
  author: 'PlayerStall',
  slug: 'lockers-for-sale',
  wordCount: 627
};

const content = `<h1>If you are looking for lockers for sale, you've come to the right place!</h1>
PlayerStall Sports Lockers has had lockers for sale for over 3 decades and continues to be the market leader in producing the highest quality <em>wood lockers</em> in the business. There are a few things that set us apart from the wood locker competition:
<ul>
